MacroHedgeExecutorOnResultTest::decodeAndAuth
├── when the platform delivers a response whose result is an abi encoded HedgeLegParams
│   ├── it should decode the result bytes into a well formed HedgeLegParams
│   └── it should route the decoded params to the mint sink
├── when a callback caller is not the platform
│   └── it should revert NotPlatform
└── when an unknown or replayed requestId is delivered
    ├── given the requestId was never registered
    │   └── it should revert UnknownRequest
    └── given the requestId was already delivered and cleared by the callback
        └── it should revert UnknownRequest
